  "title": "AB03 - Early Childhood Centre Support Assistant – Cleaner & Cook",
  "description": "<p><strong>Preschool Cook cum Cleaner</strong><br /><br />Salary: up to $1,800 </p><p>Working Days & Hours: Monday to Friday, 7:30am – 4:30pm</p><p>Location: Islandwide<br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong><br />• Prepare daily meals and snacks for children and staff.<br />• Ensure food meets basic nutritional and hygiene standards.<br />• Clean and maintain the kitchen, pantry, and food preparation areas.<br />• Carry out daily cleaning of classrooms, toilets, and common areas.<br />• Replenish cleaning supplies and handle waste disposal.<br />• Assist with meal preparation during centre activities when required.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br />• Possess a food handling or food hygiene–related certificate.<br />• Have basic knowledge of food safety and hygiene.<br /></p><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
